title: 191: Turkey Day Survival Tips
description: It is Thanksgiving in the United States, a day many people celebrate by massively overeating. Whether you overeat on Thanksgiving or have other celebrations that lead you to overindulge, Sal, Adam & Justin provide some tips to getting back on track with healthy eating as quickly as possible.
